'''Turkey''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Ankara, along with Istanbul and Izmir.

There is a Turkey-based [[Achievements|achievement]] called ''"Midnight Express"'' if a character residing in Turkey gets sent to prison. It is based from the 1978 film ''Midnight Express''.
